{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Update your code from Lockman 1.2 to take advantage of Lockman 1.3’s simplified API and enhanced safety features.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/lockman\/migratingto1.3"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/MigratingTo1.3"},"kind":"article","metadata":{"title":"Migrating to 1.3","modules":[{"name":"Lockman"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lockman 1.3 introduces a major API simplification by removing the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"withLock"},{"type":"text","text":" methods in favor of the more consistent "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Effect.lock"},{"type":"text","text":" method chain approach. This change eliminates API duplication and provides a cleaner, more maintainable codebase."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The key improvements include:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removal of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"withLock"},{"type":"text","text":" methods for API consistency"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enhanced safety through automatic lock management"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Simplified learning curve with fewer API options","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Better integration with TCA’s Effect patterns"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"Updating dependencies","anchor":"Updating-dependencies","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To upgrade to Lockman 1.3, update your ","type":"text"},{"code":"Package.swift","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" file:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["dependencies: [","  .package(","    url: \"https:\/\/github.com\/takeshishimada\/Lockman\",","    from: \"1.3.0\"","  )","]"]},{"level":2,"text":"Breaking changes","anchor":"Breaking-changes","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Removal of withLock methods","anchor":"Removal-of-withLock-methods","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"withLock"},{"type":"text","text":" methods have been removed. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Effect.lock"},{"type":"text","text":" method chain or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Reducer.lock"},{"type":"text","text":" instead."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"🚫 Before (1.2):"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["return .withLock(","  operation: { send in","    try await performWork()","    await send(.completed)","  },","  catch handler: { error, send in","    await send(.failed(error))","  },","  lockFailure: { error, send in","    await send(.lockFailed)","  },","  action: action,","  boundaryId: CancelID.operation",")"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"✅ After (1.3):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["return .run { send in","  try await performWork()","  await send(.completed)","} catch: { error, send in","  await send(.failed(error))","}",".lock(","  action: action,","  boundaryId: CancelID.operation,","  lockFailure: { error, send in","    await send(.lockFailed)","  }",")"]},{"level":3,"text":"Removal of withLock(concatenating:)","type":"heading","anchor":"Removal-of-withLockconcatenating"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"withLock(concatenating:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method has been renamed to ","type":"text"},{"code":"Effect.lock(concatenating:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"🚫 Before (1.2):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["return .withLock(","  concatenating: [","    .run { send in await step1() },","    .run { send in await step2() },","    .run { send in await step3() }","  ],","  action: action,","  boundaryId: CancelID.workflow",")"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ After (1.3):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["return .lock(","  concatenating: [","    .run { send in await step1() },","    .run { send in await step2() },","    .run { send in await step3() }","  ],","  action: action,","  boundaryId: CancelID.workflow",")"]},{"level":3,"text":"Manual unlock functionality removed","type":"heading","anchor":"Manual-unlock-functionality-removed"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Manual unlock functionality (unlock parameter in operation) has been removed. All locks are now automatically managed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"🚫 Before (1.2):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["return .withLock(","  operation: { send, unlock in","    defer { unlock() }","    try await performWork()","    await send(.completed)","  },","  action: action,","  boundaryId: CancelID.operation",")"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ After (1.3):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["return .run { send in","  try await performWork()","  await send(.completed)","}",".lock(","  action: action,","  boundaryId: CancelID.operation,","  unlockOption: .immediate \/\/ Control timing instead",")"]},{"level":2,"text":"Migration strategy","type":"heading","anchor":"Migration-strategy"},{"level":3,"text":"Step 1: Replace withLock with Effect.lock","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-1-Replace-withLock-with-Effectlock"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For each "},{"code":"withLock","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Move the operation closure to a ","type":"text"},{"code":".run { }","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" effect","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Move the catch handler to "},{"code":".catch { }","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if present"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Chain ","type":"text"},{"code":".lock()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with the action and boundary parameters","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Move lockFailure to the lock method","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":3,"text":"Step 2: Replace withLock(concatenating:) calls","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-2-Replace-withLockconcatenating-calls"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Change method name from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".withLock(concatenating:"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".lock(concatenating:"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Parameters remain the same","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":3,"text":"Step 3: Remove manual unlock usage","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-3-Remove-manual-unlock-usage"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remove "},{"code":"unlock","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter from operation closures"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remove manual "},{"code":"unlock()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" calls"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"unlockOption"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter to control timing if needed"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"Complete migration examples","type":"heading","anchor":"Complete-migration-examples"},{"level":3,"text":"Basic operation migration","type":"heading","anchor":"Basic-operation-migration"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"🚫 Before (1.2):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["case .fetchData:","  return .withLock(","    operation: { send in","      let data = try await apiClient.fetchData()","      await send(.dataReceived(data))","    },","    catch handler: { error, send in","      await send(.fetchFailed(error))","    },","    lockFailure: { error, send in","      await send(.fetchBlocked)","    },","    action: action,","    boundaryId: CancelID.fetch","  )"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"✅ After (1.3):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["case .fetchData:","  return .run { send in","    let data = try await apiClient.fetchData()","    await send(.dataReceived(data))","  } catch: { error, send in","    await send(.fetchFailed(error))","  }","  .lock(","    action: action,","    boundaryId: CancelID.fetch,","    lockFailure: { error, send in","      await send(.fetchBlocked)","    }","  )"]},{"level":3,"text":"Concatenated operations migration","type":"heading","anchor":"Concatenated-operations-migration"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"🚫 Before (1.2):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["case .processWorkflow:","  return .withLock(","    concatenating: [","      .send(.workflowStarted),","      .run { send in await processStep1() },","      .run { send in await processStep2() },","      .send(.workflowCompleted)","    ],","    unlockOption: .transition,","    action: action,","    boundaryId: CancelID.workflow","  )"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ After (1.3):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["case .processWorkflow:","  return .lock(","    concatenating: [","      .send(.workflowStarted),","      .run { send in await processStep1() },","      .run { send in await processStep2() },","      .send(.workflowCompleted)","    ],","    unlockOption: .transition,","    action: action,","    boundaryId: CancelID.workflow","  )"]},{"level":3,"text":"Complex manual unlock migration","type":"heading","anchor":"Complex-manual-unlock-migration"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"🚫 Before (1.2):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["case .complexOperation:","  return .withLock(","    operation: { send, unlock in","      try await phase1()","      ","      if shouldSkipPhase2 {","        unlock()","        await send(.skipped)","        return","      }","      ","      try await phase2()","      unlock()","      await send(.completed)","    },","    catch handler: { error, send, unlock in","      unlock()","      await send(.failed(error))","    },","    action: action,","    boundaryId: CancelID.complex","  )"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ After (1.3):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["case .complexOperation:","  return .run { send in","    try await phase1()","    ","    if shouldSkipPhase2 {","      await send(.skipped)","      return","    }","    ","    try await phase2()","    await send(.completed)","  } catch: { error, send in","    await send(.failed(error))","  }","  .lock(","    action: action,","    boundaryId: CancelID.complex,","    unlockOption: .immediate \/\/ Automatic timing control","  )"]},{"level":2,"text":"Benefits of upgrading","type":"heading","anchor":"Benefits-of-upgrading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Simplified API"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Single consistent method chain approach"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enhanced safety"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Automatic lock management prevents lock leaks","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Better TCA integration"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Natural fit with Effect patterns"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reduced learning curve"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Fewer API variants to learn"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Improved maintainability","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Cleaner, more predictable code patterns"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"API mapping reference","type":"heading","anchor":"API-mapping-reference"},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Old API (1.2)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"New API (1.3)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".withLock(operation:...)","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".run {...}.lock(...)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".withLock(concatenating:...)","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".lock(concatenating:...)","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"operation: { send, unlock in }"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".run { send in }","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"code":"unlockOption","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Manual ","type":"text"},{"code":"unlock()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" calls","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Automatic with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"unlockOption"},{"text":" control","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"level":2,"text":"Testing your migration","type":"heading","anchor":"Testing-your-migration"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After migrating, verify that:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Lock behavior is maintained","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Operations are still properly locked","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Error handling works"}]},{"text":": Both operation errors and lock failures are handled","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Timing is correct"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"unlockOption"},{"text":" to adjust timing if needed","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Performance is maintained"}]},{"type":"text","text":": No regression in lock performance"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"Summary","type":"heading","anchor":"Summary"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Lockman 1.3 represents a significant API simplification while maintaining all the functionality and safety guarantees of previous versions. The migration primarily involves moving from ","type":"text"},{"code":"withLock","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to ","type":"text"},{"code":"Effect.lock","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method chains, which provides a cleaner and more consistent API surface.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways:"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Breaking changes"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": ","type":"text"},{"code":"withLock","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" methods removed","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Consistent API","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Single method chain approach with ","type":"text"},{"code":"Effect.lock","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Enhanced safety","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Automatic lock management only"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Better integration","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Natural fit with TCA Effect patterns"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The new API eliminates confusion between different locking approaches and provides a more maintainable codebase going forward."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://Lockman/documentation/Lockman":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/lockman","abstract":[{"text":"Elegant exclusive control for user actions in The Composable Architecture applications.","type":"text"}],"title":"Lockman"}}}